{"arkId":"cl010099395","url":"https:\/\/collections.louvre.fr\/ark:\/53355\/cl010099395","modified ":"2025-08-25","title":"Tabati\u00e8re","titleComplement":"","denominationTitle":[{"type":"Titre","value":"Tabati\u00e8re"}],"displayDateCreated":"Epoque \/ p\u00e9riode : Louis XV (1715-1774) (Occident-\u003E\u00e9poque moderne = Ancien R\u00e9gime-\u003Edynastie des Bourbons)\r\n\r\nDate de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication : 1756 - 1762","currentLocation":"Sully, [OArt] Salle 614 - Galerie Louis XV, Vitrine 14","room":"Salle 614, Aile Aile Sully, Niveau 1","isMuseesNationauxRecuperation":false,"dateCreated":[{"startYear":1756,"endYear":1762,"imprecision":"","text":"3e tiers du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle = dernier tiers du XVIIIe si\u00e8cle","type":"Date de cr\u00e9ation\/fabrication","doubt":""}],"creator":[{"label":"Demay, Louis-Philippe","attributionLevel":"Attribution actuelle","linkType":"","dates":[{"date":"1772","place":"Paris","type":"date de mort"}],"creatorRole":"Orf\u00e8vre","authenticationType":"","doubt":"","attributedBy":"","attributedYear":"","wikidata":""}],"objectNumber":[{"value":"OA 6835","type":"Num\u00e9ro principal"}],"collection":"D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age, de la Renaissance et des temps modernes","printsDrawingsEntity":"","printsDrawingsCollection":"","objectType":"accessoire personnel, bo\u00eete, \u00e9tui","originalObject":"","printState":"","description":"Tabati\u00e8re d\u0027or de forme ovale  aux faces enti\u00e8rement grav\u00e9es et cisel\u00e9es en ors de trois tons (jaune, vert \u0026 rose) d\u0027\u00e9coin\u00e7ons quadrill\u00e9s, de filets, de contours avec agrafes feuillag\u00e9es, le tout encadrant six tableaux \u00e9maill\u00e9s en plein et en couleurs de sc\u00e8nes d\u0027int\u00e9rieur grandement inspir\u00e9es de David T\u00e9niers le jeune. \r\nSur le couvercle : un concert \u00e0 trois villageois\r\nAu dessous : deux buveurs pr\u00e8s d\u0027un tonneau\r\nSur la b\u00e2te : une joueuse de cornemuse ; un gar\u00e7on et son canari ; un marchand de vin dans sa cave ; une petite fille buvant un potage. \r\nPilastres cisel\u00e9s d\u0027un cartouche \u00e0 coquille et \u00e0 fleuron. Bordures d\u0027encadrement en ors de m\u00eames tons accompagn\u00e9es d\u0027une frise d\u0027entrelacs ou d\u0027oves.","inscriptions":"Poin\u00e7on : \r ; Chiffre 104 (Frapp\u00e9 en creux, sur la gorge \u00e0 gauche)\r ; Coquille (1756 - 1762) (Poin\u00e7on de d\u00e9charge : sur la gorge \u00e0 droite)\r ; Herse (1756 - 1762) (Poin\u00e7on de charge : Dans le fond de la bo\u00eete, sur le revers du couvercle, sur le revers de la b\u00e2te)\r ; Lettre X (1761 - 1762) (Poin\u00e7on de maison commune : Dans le fond de la bo\u00eete, sur le revers du couvercle, sur le revers de la b\u00e2te)\r ; poin\u00e7on de ma\u00eetre orf\u00e8vre (Dans le fond de la bo\u00eete, sur le revers du couvercle, sur le revers de la b\u00e2te)","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"3,7","displayDimension":"3,7 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Largeur","value":"7,8","displayDimension":"7,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Profondeur","value":"5,8","displayDimension":"5,8 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Technique : \u00e9maill\u00e9 = \u00e9maillage = \u00e9mail = \u00e9maux (techniques m\u00e9tal)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : or\r\nTechnique : cisel\u00e9 = ciselure (techniques m\u00e9tal)","placeOfCreation":"Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection baron Basile de Schlichting (1857-1914) Paris. Legs 1914","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Baron Schlichting, Basile de","note":"","role":", Donateur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode